  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to investigate whether pre-operative dysregulated systemic lipid
      mediator pathways are associated with increased risk for the development of persistent post
      surgical pain. In addition we will investigate whether treatment with an over the counter
      dietary supplement containing a fractionated marine lipid derivative from anchovy and sardine
      oil prevents the development of chronic pain after surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
